                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18321129-20-off111 t18321129-20-cd112"></join>, 1 collar, value 6d.; 3 handkerchiefs, value 5s; 3 pair of stockings, value 18d.; 1 shirt, 2s.; 1 pot, value 2d., and 1 bottle, value 2d., the goods of 
                     
