                  </persName>
             (Police-constable C 157). On the Monday following I went to a public-house; Lyke went in and got the prisoner out - I took him; the<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183211290016"></xptr>bundle has not been found, but I have a collar, a bottle, and a small pot, which I found in a deal box at his lodging - the rest of the things are lost.</p>
